---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Daily Crusader — 365 Days of Warrior Faith" description="A devotional in your inbox every morning at 5 AM. 365 days rooted in Scripture — built to sharpen your discipline and anchor your day.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">The Daily Crusader</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">365 Days of Warrior Faith</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 2rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="crusader-content">

        <div class="crusader-intro">
          <p>
            A devotional in your inbox every morning at 5 AM. 365 days of short, direct entries rooted in Scripture —
            built to sharpen your discipline and anchor your day before the world gets a word in. No fluff. No comfort theology.
            The narrow path, one step at a time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="crusader-features">
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Daily at 5 AM</h3>
            <p>Before the noise starts. Before the enemy gets a word in. Your marching orders arrive first.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Rooted in Scripture</h3>
            <p>Every entry is anchored in the Word — not opinion, not trends, not motivational fluff.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>365 Days</h3>
            <p>This is not a weekend retreat. It's a year-long march. Step after step after step.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="crusader-cta card">
          <h2>Subscribe to The Daily Crusader</h2>
          <p>Join the march. One devotional every morning. No spam. No fluff. Just the Word.</p>
          <a href="https://crusader.thenarrowmarch.com" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="crusader-book">
          <h2>The Book</h2>
          <p class="book-title-full"><em>The Daily Crusader: 365 Days of Warrior Faith</em></p>
          <p>
            The newsletter draws from the full devotional book — a 365-day journey through Scripture
            designed for men who take their faith seriously. Each entry is forged to cut through distraction
            and anchor you in what matters.
          </p>
          <p class="coming-soon">Book availability coming soon.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding-top: 7rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .crusader-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .crusader-intro p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .crusader-features {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .feature p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .crusader-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .crusader-cta h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .crusader-cta p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .crusader-book {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .crusader-book h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .book-title-full {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .crusader-book p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coming-soon {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
